These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: asparagus, papaya
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not the person eating papaya##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | papaya   | asparagus  |
| Sport   | water-polo | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: apricot, potato
2 different pets are kept: mouse, hedgehog
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the mouse is not the person eating potato##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | apricot | potato      |
| Pet    | mouse  | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
