.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-4::.
There 2 different types of food: kale, radish
2 different pets are kept: pony, lizard
1. the person eating radish is not the owner of the pony##6
2. the person eating radish is somewhere to the right of the person eating kale##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2      |
| Food   | kale  | radish |
| Pet    | pony | lizard    |

