.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-5::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, fantasy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, swimming
1. the person watching fantasy movies is not the person who's sport is swimming##6
2. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | fantasy |
| Sport         | swimming | tennis      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-6::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, dubstep
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, australian
1. the fan hip-hop is on the far right##1
2. the fan dubstep is not the canadian##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | hip-hop      |
| Nationality   | australian | canadian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  journalist, police-officer
2 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret
1. the journalist is in an odd position##4
2. the journalist is not the owner of the ferret##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | journalist | police-officer |
| Pet   | mouse       | ferret       |

 #################################

 
